title: Ontario Building Code 2012 Volume 2
description:
Ontario Building Code 2012 Volume 2 Supplementary Standards
The OBC 2012 came into effect Jan. 1, 2014
Volume 1 is free from e-laws. 
Volume 2 was not e-accessible..... till now :)
This version is a pdf of low res bitmaps and minimal bookmarks for use on e-devices.
This document is current as of April 2014. Updates/revisions are freely available through www.publications.serviceontario.ca
The Full scan version when I get around to it.
Info on Laws we are required to obey should always be free and accessible!
